<div class="title">Sailing Into Home Base</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B & MDMA</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=2">Scotto</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Scotto. "Sailing Into Home Base: An Experience with 2C-B & MDMA (exp2049)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 23, 2000. erowid.org/exp/2049</div>

<br/>



